outputs.output_descr: The project aims at strengthening the national capacity to coordinate the national response to HIV/AIDs and enhance access to healhcare services for vulnerable groups; supporting initiatives where vulnerable groups enjoy greater access to information and support services for HIV/AIDS/STI prevention; strengthening capacities of key staff of health care system and AIDS Centers.

project_descr: Support the Government of Turkmenistan in development of new National Programme on HIV Prevention for 2012-2016
